Class Fish

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscd210Classes.Fish
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Fish>

    public class Fish
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Fish>
    A fish class that has the standard methods and allows two fish to be compared by the compareTo method.
    NOTE:
    All parameters will be passed as final, You must use this. through out the class, You must use @Override on equals, hashCode, compareTo, toString
